NAME
    Attr/Integer -- implement integer attribute using symlink 

METHODS
    set     -- set the attribute to the given integer value
    is      -- assert attribute has the given value
    show    -- print attribute value to stdout
    help    -- display this help screen

IMPLEMENTATION
    An Attr/Integer object is a symlink file with it's target set
    to a numeric value and with prefix =.  The prefix is intended to
    make collisions with actual files unlikely.

